Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:41.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被強行拷上了手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.80,0:22:47.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:52.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這定罪的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:55.02,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇異的獨角戲舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:57.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看著 競爭
